data.description: AMAZING FULLY REMODELED HOME! TURN KEY READY! A single level home nested in a quiet and friendly cul de sac. Only one of a few single level homes in the area with beautiful curb appeal. A fresh low maintenance front yard next to a relaxing shaded front porch. Walk into a bright and warming entrance through the hallway into a FULLY REMODELED KITCHEN. Soft close cabinets and drawers. With a full freshly painted interior! Beautiful white walls with natural lighting coming through. Bathrooms were fully remodeled. Wood style flooring. BRAND NEW AC UNIT JUST INSTALLED! This home is TURN KEY and is an absolutely beautiful single story home. Conveniently located in front of the Perris Fairgrounds and Lake Perris!
